{"path":"&nbsp;","async":"0","date":"2018 May 08","desc":"An encoding schema where in data is mapped to words","content":"<div id='message' class='alt_div_shade'> <div id='basis'> <span id='basis_image' class='image' title='WCode basis'><svg xmlns='http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg' x='0px' y='0px' width='480px' viewBox=\"0 0 120 44\"> <g transform=\"matrix(0.19140679,0,0,0.18378327,-55.667615,776.73049)\"> <g transform=\"translate(-319.88919,374.56503)\"> <path fill='#69b7cf' stroke='#69b7cf' d=\"M703.3-4541c19,0.3,40.6-6.2,41.6-38.1 c-8.8-0.9-34.2,3.8-36,27.7c-1.3,17.5-7.9,8.8-10.7-4.1c-4.1,1.3-1.1,0.2-6.6,2.3c13.6,22,7.1,33.4,9.7,33.2 C704.3-4520.2,703.4-4530.3,703.3-4541L703.3-4541L703.3-4541z\"\/> <path fill='#ffffff' stroke-width='3px' stroke='#69b7cf' stroke-linejoin='round' d=\"M631.1-4504.7c-32.2,29.2-21,108.7,36.9,131.2c12.2,4.3,19.5-7.1,42.6,4.1c8.1,3.9,17.1-1.2,26.3-7.3c9.1-6,12.3-9.2,16.5-12.6 c16.7-15.3,35.6-41.7,32.6-85.3c-3.5-32.5-36-68.5-84.1-41.5C688.7-4522.9,663.4-4534.4,631.1-4504.7L631.1-4504.7z\"\/> <\/g> <text transform=\"matrix(5.2245 0 0 5.4412 551.2632 -4024.2944)\" fill='#dfdfdf' font-family='Abel' font-size='35.0019px'>=<\/text> <text transform=\"matrix(5.2245 0 0 5.4412 744.6774 -4024.2944)\" fill='#69b7cf' font-family='Abel' font-size='36px'>1<\/text> <\/g> <\/svg> <\/span> <\/div> <div id='what'> <h2><span class='bullet'>&#8226;<\/span>what<\/h2> <div class='indent-60'> <span>Communicate digital information using only simple words.<\/span> <\/div> <div id='codes-example'> <div class=\"indent-60\" id='codes-table-label'>Below, each symbolize the same data; The bottom one: words enclosed by slashes, is the equivalent WCode<\/div> <div id='codes-table'> <div id='codes-table-top' class='blue'>One two three four five six<\/div> <div id='codes-table-mid'> <div><div class='code'><span id='bar-code' class='image' title='Bar Code : Rectangle with black bars'><svg xmlns='http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg' x='0px' y='0px' viewBox=\"0 0 126.3 78.9\"> <g